---
title: Classic Chicken & Veggie Traybake with Flaked Almonds & Dill-Parsley Yoghurt
description: Create a family feast of colourful veggies and succulent chicken thigh. Our Aussie spice blend brings a moreish flavour to the chicken and veggies, while the dill-parsley yoghurt is perfect for dolloping over everything. Yum!

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette was in short supply, so we've replaced it with carrot. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
